## 11. **Live Search Filter with List Output**

✅ **Goal**: Filter a list of items by name as you type.

```js
const searchTerm = Stream('');
const fullList = Stream(['Apple', 'Banana', 'Cherry', 'Avocado']);

const filteredList = derived([searchTerm, fullList], ([term, list]) =>
  list.filter(item => item.toLowerCase().includes(term.toLowerCase()))
);

const searchUI = column([
  editText(searchTerm, { placeholder: 'Search fruits...' }),

  derived(filteredList, list =>
    column(list.map(name => reactiveText(Stream(name))))
  )
], { gap: '1rem' });
```

