## 12. **Loading Spinner with Delayed Data Load**

✅ **Goal**: Simulate a fetch call and show a spinner until it completes.

```js
const data = Stream(null);
const isLoading = Stream(true);

setTimeout(() => {
  data.set({ name: 'Loaded Data' });
  isLoading.set(false);
}, 2000);

const ui = conditional(isLoading, () =>
  reactiveText(Stream('Loading...'), { size: '1.2rem' }),
  () => reactiveText(derived(data, d => `Result: ${d.name}`))
);
```

