## 13. **Inline Editable List Items**

✅ **Goal**: Render a list of items where each item can be edited in place.

```js
const items = Stream([
  { id: 1, name: 'Task A' },
  { id: 2, name: 'Task B' }
]);

const itemList = derived(items, list =>
  column(
    list.map(item => {
      const nameStream = Stream(item.name);
      return row([
        editText(nameStream),
        reactiveButton(Stream('Save'), () => {
          items.set(items.get().map(i =>
            i.id === item.id ? { ...i, name: nameStream.get() } : i
          ));
        })
      ], { gap: '1rem' });
    })
  )
);
```

