## 14. **Confirmation Modal for Destructive Action (Reusable Pattern)**

✅ **Goal**: Ask before deleting a user.

```js
const users = Stream(['Alice', 'Bob', 'Charlie']);

const ui = derived(users, list =>
  column(list.map(name => {
    return row([
      reactiveText(Stream(name)),
      reactiveButton(Stream('Delete'), async () => {
        const ok = await showConfirmationDialog(`Delete ${name}?`, currentTheme);
        if (ok) {
          users.set(users.get().filter(n => n !== name));
        }
      })
    ], { justify: 'space-between' });
  }))
);
```

