## 15. **Tab View Using Stream State**

✅ **Goal**: Toggle between views using tab buttons.

```js
const tab = Stream('info');

const tabButtons = row([
  reactiveButton(Stream('Info'), () => tab.set('info')),
  reactiveButton(Stream('Settings'), () => tab.set('settings'))
], { gap: '0.5rem' });

const tabView = derived(tab, t => {
  if (t === 'info') {
    return reactiveText(Stream('This is the info view'));
  } else {
    return reactiveText(Stream('Settings go here'));
  }
});

const ui = column([tabButtons, tabView], { gap: '1rem' });
```

