## 16. **Form with Validation and Error Feedback**

✅ **Goal**: Show errors if fields are empty before saving.

```js
const name = Stream('');
const error = Stream('');

const form = column([
  editText(name, { placeholder: 'Name' }),
  reactiveText(error, { color: 'red' }),

  reactiveButton(Stream('Submit'), () => {
    if (name.get().trim() === '') {
      error.set('Name is required');
    } else {
      error.set('');
      showToast(`Submitted: ${name.get()}`, { type: 'success' });
    }
  })
]);
```

