## 19. **Dynamic Grid With Row Selection and Highlight**

✅ **Goal**: Click on a row to highlight it.

```js
const data = Stream([
  { id: 1, title: 'A' },
  { id: 2, title: 'B' },
  { id: 3, title: 'C' }
]);

const selectedId = Stream(null);

const grid = derived(data, rows =>
  column(rows.map(row => {
    const isSelected = derived(selectedId, id => id === row.id);

    return container(
      reactiveText(Stream(row.title)),
      {
        bg: derived(isSelected, selected => selected ? '#aae' : '#eee'),
        padding: '0.5rem',
        border: '1px solid #ccc',
        margin: '0.25rem 0'
      }
    );
  }))
);
```

